313
00:28:17,894 --> 00:28:19,273
Ten chalan zomrel?

314
00:28:21,676 --> 00:28:23,290
Zomrel na polámané väzy.

315
00:28:24,960 --> 00:28:29,522
Bola to detská potýčka, ale niekto pritom umrel.

316
00:28:30,801 --> 00:28:34,201
Cheng Qingmu sa zmenil život o 180 stupňov.

317
00:28:35,585 --> 00:28:37,060
Ale nakoniec

318
00:28:38,947 --> 00:28:42,503
